reviewText: Unlike most horror films today, this film is not "JUST GORY, NO STORY" with a trite story line.  Lionsgate and Clive Barker are bad about "JUST GORY, NO STORY". When I see these names I usually pass on the movie even though I`m and avid horror fan. This film (STRICKEN) is different and worth seeing.  Oh, for the good old days when they knew how to make good horror.
